e: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">#############################################################################################################################################################################################################</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">更新2018-11-30</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">#############################################################################################################################################################################################################</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">修改的问题：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　1、可使用的最新数据库文件地址:<a title=\"最新数据库文件\" href=\"https://github.com/jiechengyang/jcycms/blob/master/data/yii2_jcycms-2018-11-30.sql\" target=\"_blank\" data-mce-href=\"https://github.com/jiechengyang/jcycms/blob/master/data/yii2_jcycms-2018-11-30.sql\">https://github.com/jiechengyang/jcycms/blob/master/data/yii2_jcycms-2018-11-30.sql</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　2、控制台创建初始化超级管理员账号</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　3、重写yii2验证码（本次重写非常简单，只是将创建的源码提出来，在自己的类里面加入了数字，后续可在基础上完全重写成自己的验证码）</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　4、demo账户的权限已经更新</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">存在的问题：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　1、<span data-mce-style=\"background-color: #00ff00;\" style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 255, 0);\">权限控制bug，最近发现的bug就是根据权限生成菜单的代码导致生成的菜单顺序不对-------后期重点修改</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　2、资源加载慢----考虑cdn</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、未完成的功能----尽快写</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、学习markdown---学习markdown</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">#############################################################################################################################################################################################################</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">更新2019-02-19</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">#############################################################################################################################################################################################################</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">修改的问题：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　1、完善文章管理，加入图片裁剪、图片水印</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　2、开始套写前端模板</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">存在的问题：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　1、系统整站测试</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　2、资源加载慢---由于本站点是香港服务器暂时无法解决</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　3、未完成的功能（采集网页、加入cdn模拟代码块、单元测试代码块）</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">预告：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　完善该系统的同时，将会把近期学习并用于实际的混合app开发写成文档，本次混合app使用的是&nbsp; cordova + app framework7Vue + yii2&nbsp;resultful</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　如果有遇到做H5App的小伙伴，小编极力推荐使用国产的uniapp（<a title=\"uniapp\" href=\"http://uniapp.dcloud.io/\" target=\"_blank\" data-mce-href=\"http://uniapp.dcloud.io\">http://uniapp.dcloud.io</a>），与framework7Vue 相似都采用了vue，但国内开发利于参看文档，而且uniapp功能更强大，跨平台更好</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">#############################################################################################################################################################################################################</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">更新2019-06-25 beta-1.0.3</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">#############################################################################################################################################################################################################</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">修改的问题：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">　　1、完善文件上传</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大概几天前收到了服务器的提示信息，站点被挂马了，还是大马文件。难受，立马去服务器上找这个文件，发现是大概一年以前的上传上来的。仔细一想，当时系统写了个粗略，为了学习yii2框架，在之后的一段时间都没有去碰系统。<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;真是教训啊，没写好的垃圾代码也敢放到公网上去，真以为大神不找你哦，仅以此次事件来警示我的职业生涯不能犯低级错误。<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;通过本次木马程序，对上传作了如下更新：<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;①优化代码，统一上传方法。（<span style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">之前的版本的代码对上传写的很错乱，搞了几个文件，这次静下心来，重置了代码，将系统里面的两种上传方式（ajax上传和post表单提交）统一到一起。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;值得注意的是，客户端针对两个上传都是使用html5 的 fromData上传，并没有使用base64数据流上传，系统在最初的时候是使用的base64上传，可以在系统里面的注释找到部分代码。放弃base64是因为它传输到web server 是字符串， 对于大文件传输会受到影响 ， php用变量接收也可能导致内存溢出等问题，所以上传改成form表单blob二进制传输较好。</span>）<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;②加入防修改文件后缀检测。（对于一些恶意的操作：将脚本文件修改为图片格式，然后上传到服务器，然后读取文件内容）<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;③优化前端有关于上传的js（注意：这里的js还未优化好，可能存在一些bug，bug出现的情况多数是：选文件、删文件、再选文件...多次操作）<br/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">　　2、静态资源压缩</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">预告：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;针对上传，后期后引入webuploader 并配合加入文件分片上传；接着使用七牛云，我已经申请了个人开发账号</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `byt_article_content` (`id`, `article_id`, `content`) VALUES
(67, 16, '<p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　时间：2018年10月26日晚8点54分49秒</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　事件：历时一段时间加上自己的拖延症，终于决定发布JCYCMS 1.0【适合初级php开发者刚入门yii2】版本啦（此处应该有掌声）！</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　注意事项：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　　　　　1、目前发布的这个版本权限配置尚未完成，因此提供出来的账号只能看到很少的菜单，后期时间会完善。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　　　　　2、系统扔处于开发阶段，未完成的和问题肯定会有，小的我发布出来的原因是 得到外界的反馈，吸取经验，提高代码质量....</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　　　　　3、由于后期完善时间不确定，有朋友想看后台很完善的功能的，qq:2064320087，我会给出管理员账号。需要者且不能随意删除重要记录</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　　　　　4、系统参考与&nbsp;<a title=\"feehicms\" href=\"http://www.feehi.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-mce-href=\"http://www.feehi.com\">feehicms</a>,公司内部系统，感谢感谢！</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　参看取码：前台:<a href=\"http://jcycms.boomyang.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" data-mce-href=\"http://jcycms.boomyang.cn\">jycms.boomyang.cn</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　　　　　　后台:<a href=\"http://backend.boomyang.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" data-mce-href=\"http://backend.boomyang.cn\">backend.boomyang.cn</a>(<span data-mce-style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: 18px;\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>账号:demo,密码:666666</strong></span>)</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　　　　　　GitHub:<a href=\"https://github.com/jiechengyang/jcycms\" target=\"_blank\" data-mce-href=\"https://github.com/jiechengyang/jcycms\">https://github.com/jiechengyang/jcycms</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　效果展示图(部分功能)：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　　　　　　　<img src=\"https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/990003/201810/990003-20181026210624196-87058109.png\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/990003/201810/990003-20181026210624196-87058109.png\" data-mce-style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" style=\"border: 0px; cursor: default; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/990003/201810/990003-20181026210726426-159000394.png\" alt=\"\" data-mce-src=\"https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/990003/201810/990003-20181026210726426-159000394.png\" style=\"border: 0px; cursor: default;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helveti